        "title": "Add OpenTelemetry LLM content spans",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Add an explicit diagnostic LLM content-capture policy for model-call diagnostics.\r\n- Attach Codex and Pi model-call prompt history, output messages, system prompt, and tool definitions when OTEL content capture is enabled.\r\n- Export OpenTelemetry-readable LLM attributes, including `gen_ai.input.messages`, `gen_ai.output.messages`, `gen_ai.system_instructions`, `gen_ai.tool.definitions`, `input.value`, and `output.value`.\r\n- Add focused tests and a changelog entry.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1465\" height=\"835\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a0c081b4-e8e4-4191-8650-7b9b609d16b7\" />\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n\r\n- `OPENCLAW_TEST_PROJECTS_SERIAL=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/diagnostic-llm-content.test.ts src/agents/pi-embedded-runner/run/attempt.model-diagnostic-events.test.ts extensions/diagnostics-otel/src/service.test.ts extensions/codex/src/app-server/run-attempt.test.ts`\r\n  - Manually tested end to end\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof\r\n\r\nBehavior addressed: OpenTelemetry LLM spans now expose prompt history, system instructions, model output, and tool definitions when `diagnostics.otel.captureContent` is explicitly enabled.\r\n",
